  "title": "2019 春 歐洲之旅 &#8211; 行程之一 &#8211; 紐倫堡",
  "excerpt": "<p>第一次寫遊記，不太確定要怎麼開始，就先用流水帳的形式來記錄這次的旅程吧。 這次的飛機是 2019/03/24 &#8230;</p>\n",
  "feature_image_url": "https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8111-e1555244590894.jpg",
  "content": "\n<p>第一次寫遊記，不太確定要怎麼開始，就先用流水帳的形式來記錄這次的旅程吧。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>這次的飛機是 2019/03/24 去 2019/04/06 回，總共約 12 天。這段期間去了三個國家：德國、捷克、奧地利。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>這一篇只有 3/25 這一天的行程，其他的我之後會慢慢補。</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"googlemaps\">\n\t\t\t\t<iframe width=\"700\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\"  src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d166052.25657243346!2d10.992953384772505!3d49.436008950710615!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x479f57aeb5b61cd3:0xdd5daf85a98c21b7!2sNuremberg,%20Germany!5e0!3m2!1sen!2stw!4v1555597670157!5m2!1sen!2stw\"></iframe>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n<!--more-->\n\n\n\n<h2>下飛機 @ 法蘭克福 Frankfurt am Main</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>3/24 晚上的飛機，到德國法蘭克福的時間約是 3/25 早上六點多，因為有過上次穿牛仔褲搭飛機不太好的經驗，這次就穿比較舒服的褲子搭機，覺得舒爽。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>領完行李之後，我們就從 Terminal 2 搭到 Terminal 1，準備搭上前往紐倫堡的 ICE。不過因為當初很怕趕不上，換車時間抓得比較寬裕， 結果就是我們在等車的地方等了 1.5 個小時，而且抵達的時間還誤點了約 30 分鐘。😂</p>\n\n\n\n<p>車上其實沒什麼特別的，就是慢慢坐。因為我們有買網路卡，所以偶爾就滑滑手機，偶爾在一些看起來比較鄉下的地方會斷訊，這邊我也錄了<a href=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8105.mov\">縮時</a>。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>就這樣一路醒醒睡睡、睡睡醒醒、滑滑手機、發發呆，我們就在十二點半到達紐倫堡了。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8160-e1555241256159.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-699\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8160-e1555241256159.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8160-e1555241256159-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption>紐倫堡中央車站</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>四處走走 @ 紐倫堡 Nürnberg</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>到達紐倫堡的第一件事就是去 check-in，我們是住在城內的 Five Reason Hostel，距離紐倫堡中央車站約走路十分鐘的路程。</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&#091;googlemaps https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d6704.647472880327!2d11.07101668757623!3d49.447294937971236!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x479f57a80e9051cb%3A0xab53e9aee03e248d!2sFive+Reasons!5e0!3m2!1szh-TW!2sfr!4v1555241454379!5m2!1szh-TW!2sfr&amp;w=700&amp;h=500]</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>這邊有個 pro tip：拉著行李箱的話，建議先在城外走到下一個路口再轉進去。不然城內的石子路會讓拖行李這件事變得十分勞苦。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>或是也可以直接搭 U-Bahn 到下一站 Opernhaus，出站後再走去 Hostel 會十分省時省力。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>放完行李後我們就穿過 pegnitz river 內的 shopping area，直接往河外走去吃了紐倫堡的百年香腸店：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/e17UmWd7tAm\">Bratwursthäusle bei St. Sebald</a>。</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow aligncenter\" data-effect=\"slide\"><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_container swiper-container\"><ul class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_swiper-wrapper swiper-wrapper\"><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-702\" data-id=\"702\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8171-e1555241359446.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8171-e1555241359446.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8171-e1555241359446-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption\">Bratwursthäusle bei St. Sebald 外觀照</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"933\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-700\" data-id=\"700\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8168-e1555238842643.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8168-e1555238842643.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8168-e1555238842643-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption\">德國啤酒</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"933\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-701\" data-id=\"701\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8169-e1555238817550.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8169-e1555238817550.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8169-e1555238817550-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption\">香腸們</figcaption></figure></li></ul><a class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-prev swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white\" role=\"button\"></a><a class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-next swiper-button-next swiper-button-white\" role=\"button\"></a><a aria-label=\"Pause Slideshow\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-pause\" role=\"button\"></a><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_pagination swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-white\"></div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>我們都覺得香腸有點太鹹，而剛好桌上有放麵包，就一人拿一個來配著吃。結果結帳時才發現一個麵包 1.1 歐元。😂我們也有點他們的 potato soup，蠻好喝的，有機會來這的話可以喝一下。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>吃完午餐後，因為身上的感覺實在太不舒服，我們就先回去旅社洗澡了。重新出門大約是下午四點左右，我們先去附近的 REWE city 買了水喝，然後在城堡內的幾個景點晃了晃。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>晃著晃著就跑到高處，景色很漂亮，可以眺望遠方。</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow aligncenter\" data-effect=\"slide\"><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_container swiper-container\"><ul class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_swiper-wrapper swiper-wrapper\"><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-705\" data-id=\"705\" src=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8185-e1555241376382.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8185-e1555241376382.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8185-e1555241376382-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-706\" data-id=\"706\" src=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8186-e1555241384332.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8186-e1555241384332.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8186-e1555241384332-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-707\" data-id=\"707\" src=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8188-e1555241393443.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8188-e1555241393443.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8188-e1555241393443-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-708\" data-id=\"708\" src=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8189-e1555241401364.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8189-e1555241401364.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8189-e1555241401364-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></li></ul><a class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-prev swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white\" role=\"button\"></a><a class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-next swiper-button-next swiper-button-white\" role=\"button\"></a><a aria-label=\"Pause Slideshow\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-pause\" role=\"button\"></a><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_pagination swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-white\"></div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>看到這景色真的身心舒暢，照片拍起來感覺不太出來有點可惜。在欣賞美景時旁邊還有別的觀光客走過來，他看到整個景色時也是直接驚呼好大一聲「WOW」。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>沒幾分鐘，莫名有一大群人衝上來（約二三十個），後面隨之有一陣雨滴很大的雨也一起湧過來，我們便離開去 <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/9u6eq3aJfNt\">Burgwächter</a> 吃豬肩了。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8191-e1555241414464.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-711\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8191-e1555241414464.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8191-e1555241414464-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption>女友點了超好喝的 Radler，我則因為天氣太冷而點了熱巧克力。</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>因為我們去的時間大約五點左右，根本還不到吃飯時間，所以店裡空蕩蕩的、沒什麼人。不過也可能因為是空閒時段，所以他們的工作人員會在室內抽煙，若會在意的話可能要注意一下。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>上面那張圖的右下盤中有個黃色的球狀物，就是許多台灣人害怕的 potato dumpling，吃起來很像濕濕的麻糬，但又沒有任何味道。我們兩人一起努力吃了半顆之後還是受不了那個感覺就放棄不吃了。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>豬肩的份量很多，也有可能是因為我們太晚吃午餐又太早吃晚餐的關係。XD</p>\n\n\n\n<p>吃完之後因為還沒天暗，我們就邊走回去邊繼續四處晃晃，也去 shopping area 裡面逛了逛，逛完就回去旅社，第一天就這樣結束了。</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow aligncenter\" data-effect=\"slide\"><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_container swiper-container\"><ul class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_swiper-wrapper swiper-wrapper\"><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"933\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-722\" data-id=\"722\" src=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8177-e1555242317535.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8177-e1555242317535.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8177-e1555242317535-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption\">Der Hase</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"933\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-723\" data-id=\"723\" src=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8178-e1555242320524.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8178-e1555242320524.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8178-e1555242320524-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption\">紐倫堡的街景</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-724\" data-id=\"724\" src=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8193-e1555242322109.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8193-e1555242322109.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8193-e1555242322109-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption\">紐倫堡的街景</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"700\" height=\"933\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-725\" data-id=\"725\" src=\"http://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8194-e1555242325814.jpg\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8194-e1555242325814.jpg 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/IMG_8194-e1555242325814-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption\">主市集廣場 Hauptmarkt 旁的大教堂 The Church of Our Lady</figcaption></figure></li></ul><a class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-prev swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white\" role=\"button\"></a><a class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-next swiper-button-next swiper-button-white\" role=\"button\"></a><a aria-label=\"Pause Slideshow\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-pause\" role=\"button\"></a><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_pagination swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-white\"></div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>結語</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>第一天感覺蠻空、蠻 Free 的，主要是因為花了大半時間在交通上，而且剛下飛機的那天狀態還不太好，排行程時可以排得ㄌㄤ一點，比較不會想吐血。</p>\n"
}